                             <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Ridley-Ignite-GTX-5-970x647.webp\" alt=\"Ridley Ignite GTX\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Ridley-Ignite-GTX-5-970x646.webp 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Ridley-Ignite-GTX-5-300x200.webp 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Ridley-Ignite-GTX-5-768x512.webp 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Ridley-Ignite-GTX-5-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Ridley-Ignite-GTX-5-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Ridley-Ignite-GTX-5-750x500.webp 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Ridley-Ignite-GTX-5-1140x760.webp 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Ridley-Ignite-GTX-5-465x310.webp 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Ridley-Ignite-GTX-5-620x413.webp 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/Ridley-Ignite-GTX-5-350x233.webp 350w\" /><figcaption>Ridley </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>No mention of a dropper seatpost, although we’re sure there’s scope to add one.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can customise the rest of the bike’s spec, with Ridley quoting prices starting at €2,799. It’s available in sizes S, M, L and XL, with Ridley recommending that riders size down from their preferred MTB sizing or stay in line with their gravel bike size.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The ‘1990s MTB with drop bars’ argument is getting difficult to ignore now, with the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/3t-extrema-italia-gravel-bike-review\">3T Extrema Italia</a>, for example, offering similar tyre clearance and the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/mason-cycles-insider\">Mason ISO</a> heading up to 2.6 inches. And Continental launched the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/new-continental-terra-adventure-tyre-blurs-the-line-between-gravel-and-mtb\">Terra Adventure gravel bike tyre</a> just this week. Conti’s gravel tyre has an XC MTB-style casing and tread and comes in widths up to 700c x 55mm. That’s 29 inches x 2.2 inches for the mountain biker.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/newsletters\"><img width=\"970\" height=\"351\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-970x351.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-970x351.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-300x109.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-768x278.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-1536x556.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-2048x741.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-750x271.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-1140x412.jpg 1140w\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/ridley-ignite-gtx\">An MTB with drop bars? Ridley launches the Ignite GTX</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Pnorman","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"59177707a16b1397a77672f98558557627347a539607da270f7ab262a9aff5e9","category":"Cycling"}